SELECT ibb_User__dlm.Id__c AS id_officer__c, MAX(SubQuery1.media_qtd_tempo_acao_atac__c) AS media_qtd_tempo_acao_atac__c, MAX(SubQuery2.media_qtd_tempo_acao_officer) AS media_qtd_tempo_acao_officer__c FROM ibb_Opportunity__dlm JOIN ibb_User__dlm ON ibb_Opportunity__dlm.OwnerUserId__c = ibb_User__dlm.Id__c JOIN ( SELECT ibb_Opportunity__dlm.OpportunityStageId__c AS opp_stage, ROUND( ABS( AVG( DATEDIFF ( ibb_Opportunity__dlm.CloseDate__c, ibb_Opportunity__dlm.CreatedDate__c ) ) ), 1 ) AS media_qtd_tempo_acao_atac__c FROM ibb_Opportunity__dlm WHERE ibb_Opportunity__dlm.OpportunityStageId__c = 'Ganha' AND ibb_Opportunity__dlm.OpportunityTypeId__c = 'Oferta' GROUP BY ibb_Opportunity__dlm.OpportunityStageId__c ) AS SubQuery1 ON ibb_Opportunity__dlm.OpportunityStageId__c = SubQuery1.opp_stage JOIN ( SELECT ibb_Opportunity__dlm.OwnerUserId__c AS id_officer, ROUND( ABS( AVG( DATEDIFF ( ibb_Opportunity__dlm.CloseDate__c, ibb_Opportunity__dlm.CreatedDate__c ) ) ), 1 ) AS media_qtd_tempo_acao_officer FROM ibb_Opportunity__dlm WHERE ibb_Opportunity__dlm.OpportunityStageId__c = 'Ganha' AND ibb_Opportunity__dlm.OpportunityTypeId__c = 'Oferta' GROUP BY ibb_Opportunity__dlm.OwnerUserId__c ) AS SubQuery2 ON ibb_Opportunity__dlm.OwnerUserId__c = SubQuery2.id_officer GROUP BY ibb_User__dlm.Id__c

SELECT ssot__Individual__dlm.ssot__Id__c as IndividualId__c, FIRST(sub1.id_campanha__c) as id_campanha__c FROM (SELECT ssot__Individual__dlm.ssot__Id__c as IndividualId__c, case when Tabela_Visao_Propensao__dlm.NOM_PROD_PRPS__c = 'Cartão DWP AZUL' and Tabela_Visao_Propensao__dlm.C_digo_Cluster__c in ('1', '2') then 'dwp azul alta renda' when Tabela_Visao_Propensao__dlm.NOM_PROD_PRPS__c = 'Cartão DWP AZUL' and Tabela_Visao_Propensao__dlm.C_digo_Cluster__c in ('3', '4', '5', '6', '7', '8') then 'dwp azul moderado' when Tabela_Visao_Propensao__dlm.NOM_PROD_PRPS__c = 'Cartão DWP GPA' and Tabela_Visao_Propensao__dlm.C_digo_Cluster__c = '4' then 'dwp gpa meia cura' when Tabela_Visao_Propensao__dlm.NOM_PROD_PRPS__c = 'Cartão DWP GPA' and Tabela_Visao_Propensao__dlm.C_digo_Cluster__c = '2' then 'dwp gpa dionisio' when Tabela_Visao_Propensao__dlm.NOM_PROD_PRPS__c = 'Cartão DWP GPA' and Tabela_Visao_Propensao__dlm.C_digo_Cluster__c = '3' then 'dwp gpa mestre cervejeiro' when Tabela_Visao_Propensao__dlm.NOM_PROD_PRPS__c = 'Cartão DWP GPA' and Tabela_Visao_Propensao__dlm.C_digo_Cluster__c in ('0', '1') then 'dwp gpa faraway' when Tabela_Visao_Propensao__dlm.NOM_PROD_PRPS__c = 'Cartão DWP GPA' and Tabela_Visao_Propensao__dlm.C_digo_Cluster__c = '5' then 'dwp gpa heavy user' when Tabela_Visao_Propensao__dlm.NOM_PROD_PRPS__c = 'Cartão DWP Latam' then 'dwp latam' when Tabela_Visao_Propensao__dlm.Indicador_Potencial_Cliente_GPA__c = '0' then 'dwp extra' when Tabela_Visao_Propensao__dlm.NOM_PROD_PRPS__c in ('Abre Contas', 'Cluster Cartões') and ssot__Individual__dlm.C_digo_Agrupamento_Grupo_Cr_dito__c in ('TARGET', 'SUPER TARGET') and Informa_es_De_Produtos_Do_Cliente__dlm.cod_chav_coro_clie__c is null then 'crossfeat cross' when Tabela_Visao_Propensao__dlm.NOM_PROD_PRPS__c != 'Abre Contas' and Tabela_Visao_Propensao__dlm.NOM_PROD_PRPS__c = 'Cluster Cartões' and ssot__Individual__dlm.C_digo_Agrupamento_Grupo_Cr_dito__c in ('TARGET', 'SUPER TARGET') and Informa_es_De_Produtos_Do_Cliente__dlm.cod_chav_coro_clie__c is null then 'crossfeat +cartao' when Tabela_Visao_Propensao__dlm.NOM_PROD_PRPS__c = 'Abre Contas' and Tabela_Visao_Propensao__dlm.NOM_PROD_PRPS__c != 'Cluster Cartões' and ssot__Individual__dlm.C_digo_Agrupamento_Grupo_Cr_dito__c in ('TARGET', 'SUPER TARGET') and Informa_es_De_Produtos_Do_Cliente__dlm.cod_chav_coro_clie__c is null then 'crossfeat +conta' when Tabela_Visao_Propensao__dlm.NOM_PROD_PRPS__c = 'Abre Contas' and Informa_es_De_Produtos_Do_Cliente__dlm.cod_chav_coro_clie__c is null then 'propensos só conta (alvo)' when ssot__Individual__dlm.C_digo_Agrupamento_Grupo_Cr_dito__c in ('TARGET', 'SUPER TARGET') and (Informa_es_De_Produtos_Do_Cliente__dlm.Classif_Valor_Parcela_Seguros__c is not null or Informa_es_De_Produtos_Do_Cliente__dlm.Classif_Valor_Parcela_de_Capitalizacao__c is not null or Informa_es_De_Produtos_Do_Cliente__dlm.Classif_Valor_Parcela_Veiculos__c is not null or Informa_es_De_Produtos_Do_Cliente__dlm.Classif_Valor_Parcela_Imobiliario__c is not null or Informa_es_De_Produtos_Do_Cliente__dlm.Classif_Valor_Parcela_Consignado__c is not null or Informa_es_De_Produtos_Do_Cliente__dlm.Classif_Valor_Parcela_Microcredito__c is not null or Informa_es_De_Produtos_Do_Cliente__dlm.Classif_Valor_Parcela_Crediario__c is not null) then 'modelo cachorros' when Proposta_Cartao_Credito__dlm.dia_vcto_fatu_ccre__c is null and Proposta_Cartao_Credito__dlm.dat_cada_prpt__c >= DATE_SUB(current_date(), 180) and Proposta_Cartao_Credito__dlm.nom_pace_crto__c in ('Azul', 'Bruxelas') then 'surpreendido' when ssot__Individual__dlm.C_digo_Agrupamento_Grupo_Cr_dito__c in ('TARGET', 'SUPER TARGET') and tbhf9009_data_ppec_coph_dlm__dlm.ind_pose_csgd__c = '1' and tbhf9009_data_ppec_coph_dlm__dlm.ind_pose_finm_veic__c = '1' and tbhf9009_data_ppec_coph_dlm__dlm.ind_pose_crdi__c = '1' and tbhf9009_data_ppec_coph_dlm__dlm.ind_pose_csrc__c = '1' and tbhf9009_data_ppec_coph_dlm__dlm.ind_pose_imol__c = '1' and tbhf9009_data_ppec_coph_dlm__dlm.ind_pose_cpsc__c = '1' and tbhf9009_data_ppec_coph_dlm__dlm.ind_pose_mcto__c = '1' then 'remains monoliner target' when tbhf9009_data_ppec_coph_dlm__dlm.ind_pose_csgd__c = '1' and tbhf9009_data_ppec_coph_dlm__dlm.ind_pose_finm_veic__c = '1' and tbhf9009_data_ppec_coph_dlm__dlm.ind_pose_crdi__c = '1' and tbhf9009_data_ppec_coph_dlm__dlm.ind_pose_csrc__c = '1' and tbhf9009_data_ppec_coph_dlm__dlm.ind_pose_imol__c = '1' and tbhf9009_data_ppec_coph_dlm__dlm.ind_pose_cpsc__c = '1' and tbhf9009_data_ppec_coph_dlm__dlm.ind_pose_mcto__c = '1' and Renda_Eleita__dlm.VLR_REND_ELTO__c > 4000 then 'remains monoliner alvo' when ssot__Individual__dlm.C_digo_Agrupamento_Grupo_Cr_dito__c in ('TARGET', 'SUPER TARGET') then 'remains prospect target' when Renda_Eleita__dlm.VLR_REND_ELTO__c > 4000 then 'remains prospect alvo' else 'none' end as id_campanha__c FROM ssot__Individual__dlm LEFT JOIN Tabela_Visao_Propensao__dlm ON ssot__Individual__dlm.ssot__Id__c = Tabela_Visao_Propensao__dlm.COD_CHAV_CORO_CLIE__c LEFT JOIN Renda_Eleita__dlm ON ssot__Individual__dlm.ssot__Id__c = Renda_Eleita__dlm.COD_CHAV_CORO_CLIE__c LEFT JOIN Informa_es_De_Produtos_Do_Cliente__dlm ON ssot__Individual__dlm.ssot__Id__c = Informa_es_De_Produtos_Do_Cliente__dlm.cod_chav_coro_clie__c LEFT JOIN Proposta_Cartao_Credito__dlm ON ssot__Individual__dlm.ssot__Id__c = Proposta_Cartao_Credito__dlm.cod_chav_coro_clie__c LEFT JOIN Pre_Negado_Cartao__dlm ON ssot__Individual__dlm.ssot__Id__c = Pre_Negado_Cartao__dlm.cod_chav_coro_clie__c LEFT JOIN tbhf9009_data_ppec_coph_dlm__dlm ON ssot__Individual__dlm.ssot__Id__c = tbhf9009_data_ppec_coph_dlm__dlm.cod_chav_coro_clie__c) as sub1 INNER JOIN ssot__Individual__dlm ON ssot__Individual__dlm.ssot__Id__c = sub1.IndividualId__c WHERE sub1.id_campanha__c != 'none' GROUP BY IndividualId__c

SELECT ssot__Individual__dlm.ssot__Id__c as IndividualId__c, Pre_Aprovado_Exclusao_Comercial__dlm.COD_AGRU_PROD_ITAU_PAPR__c as CodProdPA__c, SUM( Pre_Aprovado_Exclusao_Comercial__dlm.Indicador_Limite_Produto_PA__c ) as ValorLimSumPA__c, MIN( Pre_Aprovado_Exclusao_Comercial__dlm.Indicador_Limite_Produto_PA__c ) as ValorLimPA__c, COUNT( Pre_Aprovado_Exclusao_Comercial__dlm.id__c ) as RowCount__c FROM Pre_Aprovado_Exclusao_Comercial__dlm INNER JOIN ssot__Individual__dlm ON (Pre_Aprovado_Exclusao_Comercial__dlm.COD_CHAV_CORO_CLIE__c = ssot__Individual__dlm.ssot__Id__c) WHERE Pre_Aprovado_Exclusao_Comercial__dlm.COD_AGRU_PROD_ITAU_PAPR__c = '040' GROUP BY IndividualId__c, CodProdPA__c
SELECT Sugestao_CNPJ__dlm.cod_chav_coro_clie__c AS IndividualId__c, MAX(RAND()) AS RANDOM__c FROM Sugestao_CNPJ__dlm GROUP BY IndividualId__c

SELECT Recuperacao_de_Credito_PF__dlm.Codigo_Unico__c AS Codigo_Unico__c, FIRST(Recuperacao_de_Credito_PF__dlm.cod_chav_coro_clie__c) AS cod_chav_coro_clie__c, FIRST(Recuperacao_de_Credito_PF__dlm.id_campanha__c) AS id_campanha__c, FIRST(Recuperacao_de_Credito_PF__dlm.cod_prod_lgdo__c) AS cod_prod_lgdo__c, FIRST(Recuperacao_de_Credito_PF__dlm.dat_ulti_atrs__c) AS dat_ulti_atrs__c, FIRST(Recuperacao_de_Credito_PF__dlm.dat_inio_cobr__c) AS dat_inio_cobr__c, FIRST(Recuperacao_de_Credito_PF__dlm.dat_vcto_ctrt__c) AS dat_vcto_ctrt__c, FIRST(Recuperacao_de_Credito_PF__dlm.Dat_Vcto_Parc__c) AS Dat_Vcto_Parc__c, FIRST(Recuperacao_de_Credito_PF__dlm.num_ctrt_prod_opcr__c) AS num_ctrt_prod_opcr__c, FIRST(Recuperacao_de_Credito_PF__dlm.Qtd_Dia_Atrs__c) AS Qtd_Dia_Atrs__c, FIRST(Recuperacao_de_Credito_PF__dlm.qtd_parc_atrs_aber_ctrt__c) AS qtd_parc_atrs_aber_ctrt__c, FIRST(Recuperacao_de_Credito_PF__dlm.qtd_parc_pago_ctrt__c) AS qtd_parc_pago_ctrt__c, FIRST(Recuperacao_de_Credito_PF__dlm.vlr_divi_ctrt__c) AS vlr_divi_ctrt__c, FIRST(Recuperacao_de_Credito_PF__dlm.vlr_parc_opcr__c) AS vlr_parc_opcr__c, FIRST(Recuperacao_de_Credito_PF__dlm.vlr_sald_atul__c) AS vlr_sald_atul__c, MAX(SUB1.promessa__c) AS promessa__c FROM ( SELECT Promessas_Op_Recuperacao_Credito_Cli__dlm.cod_chav_coro_clie__c AS cod_chav_coro_clie__c, CASE WHEN datediff(Promessas_Op_Recuperacao_Credito_Cli__dlm.dat_vcto_titl__c, CURRENT_DATE()) > -15 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS promessa__c FROM Promessas_Op_Recuperacao_Credito_Cli__dlm ) AS SUB1 INNER JOIN Recuperacao_de_Credito_PF__dlm ON Recuperacao_de_Credito_PF__dlm.cod_chav_coro_clie__c = SUB1.cod_chav_coro_clie__c GROUP BY Recuperacao_de_Credito_PF__dlm.Codigo_Unico__c
